            <h2>What drain repairs actually solves</h2>
            <p>Commercial drain repairs target the section of the line that keeps catching debris or has a failed section. Cabling and jetting will not fix a separated joint, a sagging horizontal run, or a corroded section — those need pipe work.</p><p>Honest Drain inspects, scopes, and prices the repair before any tools come out. Work is staged to protect operations and finishes when it has to happen during business hours, and after-hours scheduling is available for sensitive spaces.</p>
